OL,3,CAccountability gaps amid 'rising anti-
OL,4,Cmigrant sentiment', report finds
OL,6,FDr Ebun Joseph's annual report on the
OL,7,FNational Action Plan Against Racism,
OL,8,Fpublished on Wednesday, also calls for
OL,9,Fexplicit recognition of anti-black
OL,10,Fracism in line with EU standards and a
OL,11,Freaffirmation of whole-of-Government
OL,12,Fresponsibility for racism.
OL,14,FSeven of 18 Government departments did
OL,15,Fnot submit monitoring reports to the
OL,16,Frapporteur and cited limited direct
OL,17,Fresponsibility.
OL,19,FThe report says this weakens the whole-
OL,20,Fof-Government intention of the plan.
