OL,3,CAccountability gaps amid 'rising anti-
OL,4,Cmigrant sentiment', report finds
OL,6,FThe Departments of Agriculture,
OL,7,FClimate, Defence, Finance, Foreign
OL,8,FAffairs, Taoiseach, and Transport
OL,9,Freported that they had no direct role
OL,10,Fin implementing the NAPAR.
OL,12,FHowever, the special rapporteur said
OL,13,Fthis overlooks the whole-of-Government
OL,14,Fdesign of the action plan, which
OL,15,Fplaces obligations on all public
OL,16,Fauthorities, all Government
OL,17,Fstructures, and all public sector
OL,18,Femployers around interpreting
OL,19,Fservices, reviews of legislation, and
OL,20,Fanti-racism training.
