OL,3,CAccountability gaps amid 'rising anti-
OL,4,Cmigrant sentiment', report finds
OL,6,FDr Joseph said: "Ireland has
OL,7,Festablished an important framework to
OL,8,Faddress racism.
OL,10,F"However, the first year of monitoring
OL,11,Fshows that implementation remains
OL,12,Fprocedural rather than transformative.
OL,14,F"The weaknesses identified ` including
OL,15,Funeven departmental engagement and
OL,16,Fgaps in accountability ` require
OL,17,Fstronger leadership, sustained
OL,18,Fresourcing, and full buy-in across
OL,19,FGovernment to ensure that commitments
OL,20,Ftranslate into real change in people's
OL,21,Feveryday lives."
