OL,3,CAccountability gaps amid 'rising anti-
OL,4,Cmigrant sentiment', report finds
OL,6,FThe report states that rising anti-
OL,7,Fmigrant sentiment posed a threat and
OL,8,Farose out of attacks on international
OL,9,Fprotection applicants and arson
OL,10,Fagainst accommodation centres,
OL,11,Fincreasing deportations, and mixed
OL,12,Fsignals on the benefits of migration.
OL,14,FIt said there was a growing far-right
OL,15,Fpresence and rhetoric, both online and
OL,16,Fin public spaces.
